      <title>特斯拉疯狂上涨引发估值现实考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/tesla-s-11-day-winning-run-prompts-a-valuation-reality-check</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉公司股价的强劲上涨在周四遭遇挫折，原因是有报道称该公司可能会推迟许多投资者寄予厚望的一项重要事件。然而，甚至在那之前，为多头辩护的难度就已经越来越大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/tesla-s-11-day-winning-run-prompts-a-valuation-reality-check</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 12:12:22 GMT</pubDate>
